_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$c1se_DESKTOP.1.$WRchTxta\">\r\n<h2 class=\"font_2\">OUR STORY</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"WRchTxtb\" class=\"s7\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$c1se_DESKTOP.1.$WRchTxtb\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Matsyaveda is an herbal pharmacy deeply rooted in the ancient Indian tradition of Ayurveda since 1890.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">The pharmacy’s name is inspired from \"MATSYA\" and \"AYURVEDA\". Matsya is an incarnation of the Hindu god Vishnu in the form of a fish, who rescued the first man from a catastrophic flood that destroyed all life on earth. Likewise, Matsyaveda aspires to help people recover from their ailments using natural Ayurvedic remedies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">At Matsyaveda, we firmly believe that Ayurveda brings us closer to Nature and the closer we are to Nature, the better life we can lead. We, thus offer a holistic approach to healing and wellbeing of the mind, body and soul, the natural way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Our Mission</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Matsyaveda was established to advance natural medication for people with chronic and life-threatening ailments. Since 1890, our herbal medicines have been helping patients recover from serious ailments such as nervous disorders, brain diseases, spine injuries, gastric problems, sleep disorders, rheumatism, osteo-arthritis, migraine, sexual disorders, cervical spondylitis, respiratory disorders, cancer, diabetes, heart diseases, joint pains, and many more. Apart from these, we have also prepared herbal products for general well being of people.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">We have worked tirelessly towards bringing forward formulations that are preserved in the wisdom of our ancient Indian texts. This ancient knowledge has benefited mankind around the world over centuries into this age of modern medicine.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Authenticity  Guaranteed</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Our medicines are prepared only from pure natural herbs, freshly sourced from the pristine surroundings of the Himalayas and deep forests and valleys in the country. No artificial substitute of any kind is used in our formulations, making our medicines safe and authentic. Some of these essential herbs are so rare that their availability is not always guaranteed. Thus at times we have to wait until we are able to procure such herbs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: left;\">We take great care to prepare our medicines only according to ancient Ayurvedic texts. For instance we do not use electric dryers, instead medicines are naturally sundried because many herbs lose their efficacy when subjected to artificial heat. It takes longer to sun dry, but it enhances the potency of the medicine.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:8:\"About us\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:8:\"about-us\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2016-11-14 19:12:03\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-11-14 19:12:03\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:31:\"http://www.raju.com/?page_id=54\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:4:\"page\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:62;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2016-11-14 19:24:07\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-11-14 19:24:07\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"po