e been working in tech industry around the globe. I worked with DELL in Austin Texas for couple of years and my last job was with a California based startup named \'Perspica Networks\' as a Cloud Computing and Big Data Analytics Engineer.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">I founded “Matsyaveda”, an Ayurvedic Pharmacy, under the guidance of Dr. Vijay Prakash (Ayurved Acharya) and Dr. Shobha (Yoga Acharya). I developed an inclination towards Ayurveda, Naturopathy and Yoga after i suffered a spine injury in 2004. Doctors from modern medicine had suggested me to undergo a surgery and informed me that I will have to maintain certain precautions (such as not lifting heavy bags, etc) life long. But then Yoga Acharya Dr. Shobha introduced me to Ayurveda Acharya Dr. Vijay Prakash, who is a veteran ayurvedic doctor specialising in pulse reading (nadi-shastra) to diagnose ailments. With his treatment I recovered and now even after 10 years I am living a normal life.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\">Thus since 2004, my family and friends have been using his medicines. My cousin had chronic indigestion with swelling in liver. He went to various gastroenterologist but did not find a solution. Finally he tried Dr. Vijay Prakash\'s treatment and now he is cured and his test reports shows normal liver. Similarly my uncle had pain in his right arm. He went to many allopathic doctors but the pain remain persistent. Finally he got in touch with Dr. Vijay Prakash and it came out that he has gastric problems that was causing the pain in his right arm. Now my uncle\'s arm is perfectly fine. Similarly there are many such examples.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\">Thus over a period of time I developed a firm belief in Ayurveda and decided to start this venture. Under this pharmacy we manufacture various ayurvedic medicines. The name of the pharmacy is inspired from \"MATSYA\" and \"AYURVEDA\". Matsya is an incarnation of the Hindu god Vishnu in the form of a fish, who rescued the first man from a catastrophic flood that destroyed all living beings on earth. On the same lines Matsyaveda aspires to help people recover from their ailments with Ayurveda / herbal medicines.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\">Modern lifestyle has made our lives comfortable but have detriorated our health and general well being, which I believe can be restored with help of Ayurveda and Yoga.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','An Engineer\'s journey to Ayurveda and Yoga','','publish','open','open','','an-engineers-journey-to-ayurveda-and-yoga','','','2016-11-14 19:47:18','2016-11-14 19:47:18','',0,'http://www.raju.com/?p=58',0,'post','',0),(59,1,'2016-11-14 19:18:24','2016-11-14 19:18:24','<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_def_2_child\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$0\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_WholeSinglePost\" class=\"flex_display flex_vbox\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_def_4_child\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1.$0\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"CategoriesList_MediaPost__0_0\" class=\" \" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1.$1\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_def_6\" class=\" flex_vbox\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1.$2\">\r\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_def_7\" class=\"flex_display flex_vbox\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq5