he Hindu god Vishnu in the form of a fish, who rescued the first man from a catastrophic flood that destroyed all living beings on earth. On the same lines Matsyaveda aspires to help people recover from their ailments with Ayurveda / herbal medicines.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\">Modern lifestyle has made our lives comfortable but have detriorated our health and general well being, which I believe can be restored with help of Ayurveda and Yoga.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\"></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','An Engineer\'s journey to Ayurveda and Yoga','','inherit','closed','closed','','58-revision-v1','','','2016-11-14 19:18:24','2016-11-14 19:18:24','',58,'http://www.raju.com/?p=59',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2016-11-14 19:19:43','2016-11-14 19:19:43','<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_def_2_child\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$0\"></div>\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_WholeSinglePost\" class=\"flex_display flex_vbox\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1\">\n<div id=\"innercomp_hibm2q36imgpreloader\" class=\"s15imgpreloader\" data-reactid=\".4.0.0.0\"></div>\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0__type_MediaPost\" class=\" flex_vbox\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1.$5\">\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_mediaText\" class=\"s12\" data-proxy-name=\"MediaLabel\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$odjhb_DESKTOP.1.$comp-iiq59sl53.0.0.$child.$0.1.$1.$5.$0\" data-width=\"630\">\n<div id=\"comp-iiq59sl53_SinglePostMediaTop_MediaPost__0_0_mediaTextrichTextContainer\" class=\"s12_richTextContainer s